The nursery school, too, is part of the ITPOs have understood the architects.
The administration building Avriopoint of Brno is the new headquarters of the Arch. society design.
No one would have expected that he is also a mini nursery school with all that is needed - walls of colours, imaginative furniture, toys and finally a small playground on the terrace.
Since October last year, can visit the children of employees of Arch. design.
Society of projets-architectonique Arch. design. whose workshops have produced a large number of buildings at Brno, has found its business mini nursery school since the first drafts of the building Avriopoint.
It employs about 90 people, especially from the age of children and it is important that women architects and project leaders can quickly return to work.
At the same time that work contracts in time, the nursery is a proposed bonuses to its employees by society Arch. design. within the framework of its social programme.
The builders and architects have the possibility of linking a work with the care for children.
They are employees of Arch.Design.eux-mêmes who dreamt up this nursery school and with the support of the direction they were able to obtain a contribution of the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
The mini nursery school is funded by the means of the European Social Fund through the operational programme of human resources and the state budget of the Czech Republic.
Thanks to funding allocations (to the tune of 2,8 CZK mil.de). they were able to buy equipment and appliances and after two years to ensure a qualified staff as well as the implementation.
After the use of the allocation of funding (two years) society Arch. design. has the obligation after 3 years of mini nursery school on its own funds.
The preparation of the project lasted a year and it is society Economy rating that has helped to make the staffing request.
The child care is provided by a qualified staff, the day a nurse and a teacher of tongue take care of children. a native children can go to school without age limit, but they have more than three anspour most.
As it is a "mini nursery school" there are only 5 children at the same time, but during the course of the day there are more that replace.
The operation of the school is flexible, depending on the needs of parents and children of all employees have the same right to use the school without light on the position of authority.
Although it is agise individual care and education, the programme of the mini nursery school is comparable to that for pre-school education.
Children aren't play but a quality education is also assured - from beginning to the school teaches English.
The class is equipped not only of toys and games imaginative but also of a computer that can be used by children.
The presence of small children in society creates an environment friendly and positive.
Parents may at any time control their child and not having the stress of a delay to seek children in a school from the workplace of parents.
Parents use to their working time of the most productive way.
It is not surprising that creates a natural relationship of loyalty between the employee and the employer.
Arch.design.s' is thus enshrined among the companies that offer a bonus of choice for the recruitment of new employees and which are friendly to the family and through this programme makes HR.
The house still fascinates after 100 years. domestic look in the eye of a proper talk.
The toît looks like the back of a saurien prehistoric, the stairs to a column of dinosaur and balconies to fish gueules open.
This is the house Casa Battlo in Barcelona architect Antoni proper talk.
Because of its organic forms, the house has received from the local House nickname.
Organic forms, wild colours, unusual use of stones, fragments of tiles and mosaîque, recalling facade of scales and everywhere curves, that is all that is ypique for Art Nouveau of Antoni proper talk.
The front facade of the house place its dream, its colours and textures pleasant about the nature and animals.
At a more detailed observation we see the geometry, the pace and the next thought with precision.
In the night the facade of the house becomes even more dramatic and went in such a way that the impression of brillance RGBcolor.
The enroulement and violence "is also reflected in the domestic forms with the same degree.
Timber copy in the frameworks of windows, balustrades waves, the decorative elements of the doors, the oeilleton and slats.
The house Battlo on Eixample Gracia market in the street Passeig at. 43, was born of the construction of a house of 1877 of the architect Emilio Sala Cortes.
The reconstruction has made for two years and the house completed in 1906.
The investor, Joseph Battlo, a rich businessman, was first insisted on the demolition of the vieile construction and the construction of another new but quickly accepted the idea of a proper talk of an unusual reconstruction and cheaper.
But the idea of Casa Battlo as house of which was not thought by proper talk alone.
The architect Josep Maria Jujol worked with him.
It is precisely on its project that are born the decorations for a representation of the owner of the apartment building and the use of the mosaîque for the facade.
For the façade have also worked for other artists and creators.
The joint work for the plans of the house Casa Battlo began with a proper talk and succeeding cooperation between Jujol.
Jujol participated in the construction of the house of a proper talk Casa Mila and park Guell in which there are other proper talk.
The premises have dubbed the house just after its finishing because of its organic forms "House."
Other, given the specific mechanism of opening windows have called "the house that drink."
It is said that in the top of the building there is a sword similar to that of Saint George the boss of Catalonia.
Other elements of sculpture of hidden construction contain religious grounds.
Proper talk thought for the house a single system of central heating, with évents aeration and of typical chimneys.
Their angle of 45 degrees seems odd.
During the creation proper talk has not respected the directives of construction and has not been allowed to stand by them.
At the beginning of the construction he received from the city the building permits, knowing, of course that the data on the reconstruction plans were so vague that two years after for finishing the municipal council was horrified and asked modifications.
He did not like, for example, the members of the council that the pillars of the construction empiettent on the pavement.
There was never change, but, on the contrary, only 15 days after the appeal of the city Josep Battlo (and got satisfaction) permission to praise the top two floors.
The owner moved to the lower floors.
In the gallery to the second floor there was a common living room and the third a chamber and a private part of the apartment.
The ground floor was leased to a jewellery.
The full house of six floors is shared by a staircase gives way to a terrace of toît independent.
All angles rights and straight lines were cancelled by the basic elements of the reconstruction and their replacement by walls.
Proper talk also worked the modern concept of linking spaces.
The common part can be fully connected by opening the doors of trade shows and high society can comfortably communicate or limit private space for more intimate conversations.
The house with the reconstruction of a proper talk has received a non-traditional toîture addition of new facades and two floors.
The game of proper talk with the light is also impressive, tiles, white and blue glass with which is decorated with the wells and the inner courtyard of lights.
The game in two colours gives a maximum of light in all the floors of the house.
It must simply bet on the principle that the White reflête more than the bleak instead absorbs the sun's rays.
The house Casa Battlo which in 2005 was included in the UNESCO World Heritage Fund may be used by each.
On the first floor of the house is the most spacious apartment and the most splendid accessible to the public.
The owners have decided to take this step in 2002 on the occasion of the 150 th anniversary of the birth of the famous creator.
They have continued the visits because they have found that it is a lucrative business and they have broadened the scope of the visits to the common spaces and the attic including the terraces of toît.
The entry ticket in the monument is not really expensive and costs EUR 16,50; students, pensioners, the groups and the tourist card holders have a 20 percent discount.
The sum is above the price of entry in the other constructions of proper talk in the city.
If you want to feel the real atmosphere of the house with its tourelles, you have to quickly find a comrade among the inhabitants of the building and visit the house.
How to choose a mattress and a sommier: women have other criteria than men.
Not ostentatious framework, but rather the quality of the surface for sleep, therefore the mattress and the sommier give a real basis for a good bed.
They must of course complement harmoniously to please a concrete user.
During the several things are important choice,: the weight, size, age, health status and gender of the owner.
The type in which will place the mattress and the sommier is also important.
A typical example?
For example, in the house of campaign where the mattresses are continually sleeps in gum are not appropriate because they "hot" slowly.
In addition, they have a higher weight to the standard polyurethane mattresses.
It is necessary to return frequently.
If they do not have enough channels of breakdown in and if they remain, in addition, on a solid work, they retain moisture. of the mould may also form.
The habit is also decisive in the choice.
Anyone who spends the clear of time abroad where they frequently uses very thick mattress with a layer rammollissante, is hardly on a base-income hard surface.
"that is how all the hokeyistes of NHL complain that they cannot sleep there."
"for their shoulders tired, the feet and the coasts, they needed mattress with a rammollisante layer of foam lazy."
"such mattresses are also recommended for people with diabetes who have a disorder of the nervous system who are poorly" information "of joints and skin," says Sylva Adamczikova who specializes in the furniture around.
That is why a few years ago the foam mattresses with lazy has conquered the hokeyistes and other clients.
"today everything goes well, Tempur, Italian Magnifex but also the Czech Tropico have for example, mattress.
You do not need to be a guy of NHL to appreciate a foam lazy.
This "miracle" simply working.
It make its rigidity and its form in the heat absorbed or adapts to the warmth of your body.
There is no pressure on you and you do not go back into the night and after a difficult match.
Just you sleep better.
The lazy foam also function as a protection against the esquarres.
For the choice of the mattress in your size, provide the length of the feet, or about 21 / 34 cm.
A man and a woman in a size of 180 cm have therefore need a bed of 210 / 220 cm.
The minimum width for each to a bed for two seats should be 90 cm by 180 cm.
For the singles beds in a single place, for example, it is recommended to take at least 120 / 140 cm.
It is easy in the case of visit.
"but it is a simple rule for the width of the bed: when you are lying on their backs you should ask the hands comfortable with together slightly complied. Helena Prokopova, President of the Association of Bourreliers-matelassiers and decorators who indulges for several years to the issue of a healthy sleep and ergonomics non-furniture taught in the schools.
For a bed to two places everyone needs of its own sommier and mattresses, however, therefore attention during the achât to choose the height of the mattress.
Otherwise you will increase the sommier at different heights and this is not feasible on all managers.
The foam mattress should have a minimum height of 14 cm, the mattress springs at least 15 cm, of this matter to the layer of form and aeration at least three centimetres.
"the infructueuses or in a sitting position on the mattress you should not feel the springs," warns Héléna Prokopova.
