A mattress in polyurethane must not be part of a bed of this type.
For the mattress frame to slats unique position with 14 / 18 slats, the mattress in gum or sandwiches served (perhaps the combination of gum and coconut), are the ideal, but this will always be better for you to have a mattress with more of slats, 28 and above, where the slats are doubled in the part of the kidney-sellers low and that it is possible to regulate the rigidity.
