The aircraft to follow people are increasingly requested by parents who want to monitor their children.
The fear for their child leads to more and more people to think about the monitor with a GPS.
The system, put in place at the beginning for cars can also be used to trace the movement of people and help for some cases such as exmple that of the small Anicka Janatkova.
The instrument is currently as big as a matchbox mailbox but will soon be the size of a clock.
The case of the small Anicka moved a large number of people and they have begun to seek ways to better protect their children.
Even if the price is to confuse their privacy.
"we are trying to tell everyone that it is not a question of espionage but only another way to reduce the likelihood of another tragedy," said Petr Pilin society MAcro Weil which is one of the suppliers of Czech tracing devices on the market.
"I must say that there may be cases of misuse of such devices, such as in the bag of a person who is not aware of it, but I have not yet met such cases."
"the majority of people really are clients who buy the product for security reasons," Pilin.
He said children should always know what is used "the container" and how to use in case of emergency.
The psychologist for children, Dana Bockova, draws attention if the child does not want to focus on something of this kind, it débarassera.
'And even the smallest can show a great deal of creativity when it comes to get rid of something when they do not want to be under control. "
"mobile phones, which can be cut as these devices tracing, parents have already led to long expectations," says Bockova.
She said, the fact that this type of craft can help in the event of an attack is highly questionable.
"if it is an abduction prepared, the author will do everything to ensure that the child has an electronic device that can locate him."
"it is now the phone."
"as soon as the tracing equipment, they (criminals) will also seek because the sale will be supported by an advertising campaign."
"in such cases the criminals will always be ahead of the police," says the psychologist.
It'avoue that such devices can help during an attack not prepared by a paedophile.
According to Robert Cech society RC Monitoring, which proposes tracing services both for cars and people, says that to have this kind of apparatus can help, even if it is destroyed in the case of an attack.
"the apparatus can be paramétré in such a way that he is in regular after a specified period."
"in the case where the aircraft is destroyed, it remains the position of the person concerned."
'The more expensive appliances have also inclinomètre that immediately reported the position of the person who has slipped in a recumbent position without taking any action, "said Cech.
He said the so-called smart phones that are fitted with a navigation system, can offer a comparable service after formaté with a special prologiciel.
The problem of current tracing systems is that it is a device similar to those paid in pendentif the size of a matchbox is the smaller telephone mailbox.
We can always lose.
According to the society Pilina Macro Weil, that is why the tests are being conducted for appliances that are similar to common digital watches.
"this will have the advantage that the possible aggressor will not recognize the tracing system."
"or it will report after a certain time, which would have given the police a little more time," he said.
