The US has a new "smart" weapon
The US military has sent in Afghnistan a new "smart" weapon, known only as the XM- code 25.
The generals think that this new gun autocategorizers will have an influence on the conflict with the Taliban and "will change the game" to their advantage.
The new weapon is like a super precise
Its projectiles are guided by laser with a precision of a few metres.
The 25 mm developed for this special gun and ammunition containing a highly explosive breaking, functioned as small grenades.
Ammunition in such a way that they can AJB00 will soar in the target but also at any point of their ballistic trajectory.
It can therefore be used against an enemy that hides behind a barrier, a wall or a gap.
It is not protected from above and when he is coming at a rain of shards of steel, it also can put the hors de combat.
According to Richard Audette who took part in the development of XM- 25, the new gun is the first infantry weapon that uses the 'smart' technology.
"the soldier is used mainly in such a way that it is the target, sends out a laser which determines the distance, creates a specific point of reporting, that it corrects the approach of the site and based on the trigger.
