"I am proud, as an American citizen."
"this shows that justice prevails."
"the opposition is really minimal," he added.
"they just have some very strong voices."
"we have good people in this valley."
The meeting began at 18 a.m. and lasted until nearly midnight with people, most of the time, calling for or against the COMI, speaking time almost equally distributed, according to the Press-Enterprise.
The debate has continued on the newspaper's Web site.
